Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.01,0:02:17.37,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}「肯定做不到」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:24.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}这句话已听过无数次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:30.82,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}即便装作没听到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:37.49,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}也并无区别
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.83,0:02:44.52,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我知道 是你教给我的
